  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Special Need Service for 45 Elderly People in UG</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Elderly people face several hardships in life which include chronic diseases like arthritis and disease, dental problems like tooth decay and infection, poor housing, malnutrition, stress among others. In addition to this, most of the elderly people come from poor families making it extremely hard to meet the basic necessities of life. This also puts their lives in danger. Therefore, this project will promote the well-being of elderly people.</narrative>
  </description>
